一个使用键盘灯传输数据的代码 by Blocks233
打开程序，输入一个整数/字母 回车 输入前确保所有键盘灯处于关闭状态
回车后三个键盘灯会闪烁三次，之后开始显示二进制数据
显示结束后键盘灯会再闪烁三次

核心函数 keybd_event

A code to transfer data using a keyboard light by Blocks233
Open the program and enter an integer/letter Enter. Make sure all keyboard lights are off before entering.
After the carriage return, the three keyboard lights will flash three times, then start to display binary data.
The keyboard light will flash three times after the display is over.

Core function keybd_event

